<p>
<note n="0311001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0311001">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0311002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0311002">是＝自【明】</note>
<note n="0311003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0311003">方＝有【元】</note>
<note n="0312001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312001">七＝十【元】</note>
<note n="0312002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312002">十＝七【元】</note>
<note n="0312003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312003">降伏＝降住【宮】</note>
<note n="0312004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312004">（成）＋道【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0313001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313001">啞＝瘂【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0313002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313002">奉＝拳【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0313003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313003">提＋（之）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0313004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313004">〔癡〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0313005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313005">破＝礙【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0313006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313006">惱＋（補特伽羅）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0313007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313007">〔別〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0314001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314001">為＝而【三】</note>
<note n="0314002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314002">邪道＋（者）【宮】</note>
<note n="0314003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314003">無結＝諸【宮】</note>
<note n="0315001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315001">為＝謂【宮】</note>
<note n="0315002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315002">何＋（菩薩）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0315003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315003">要＝邀【宮】</note>
<note n="0315004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315004">化＝他【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0315005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315005">不分卷【元】【明】</note>
</p>
